itude for my wife, we decided to mount ourPanasonic TC-L32X2 32-Inch 720p LCD HDTVon the wall, above the dresser, to save some space. (You can never have enough dresser space for displaying tchotchkes, amirite, fellas?) My wife wanted a fixed wall mount but I thought the viewing angle required some articulation. (In hindsight, fixed would have worked, too.) This unit was highly rated and the price was right. Sold.The installation was straightforward and fairly simple. The only point at which I needed some help was in balancing the TV while I attached it to the arm; otherwise it was all me. I think it looks great; my wife says it reminds her of being in the hospital. (Sorry, Honey.) When we mount thePanasonic VIERA TC-P42S30 42-Inch 1080p Plasma HDTVin the living room, I\'ll definitely use a flat mount.You could spend four times this much on an articulating TV mount, but I don\'t see why you would.',5,'Simple and effective. Just the way I like it.',1306886400,'06 1, 2011'),(383,'A3Q95HLHAUC34M','0972683275','cv',0,0,'This is a high quality product with a more reasonable price than offered at retail stores. Strong, durable, very practical. Definitely recommend.',5,'Great product at amazing price',1395619200,'03 24, 2014'),(384,'A3UBDM2OA2Y3I9','0972683275','C.Watts',0,0,'I was looking for a nice tv mount for my bedroom. Found this one and am more than happy with it. Great mount.',5,'Great product',1360540800,'02 11, 2013'),(385,'A1AT5LYGF3T3BJ','0972683275','Cyril 3.',1,1,'Works great, very happy with the purchased. Mounted our Vizio 40&#34; TV on the wall and has full motion. Easy to adjust and install.',4,'Works great',1393372800,'02 26, 2014'),(386,'A2VEU4GLPJUFNP','0972683275','Dabnis',0,0,'firstly, this thing is sturdy! I mean i gotta 55in sony hangin from it and even when you pull it all the way out it holds great!the only thing is the bottom 2 bars of the x shaped support stick out past the bottom of the tv and are visable. it just doesn\'t look exactly clean b