ome, cheap, easy, simple',1342915200,'07 22, 2012'),(402,'AY7Y69EUL5GGL','0972683275','David C Offerdahl',0,0,'Easy to assemble and mount/adaptable for various sized TVs/adjusts (swivel and extend) easily.  Great product especially for the price.  I would recommend to anyone!',5,'Great TV wall mount...exceeded all expectations.',1394323200,'03 9, 2014'),(403,'A31QWH1JR60A5F','0972683275','David G \"DG\"',0,0,'I purchased this mount for a 42&#34; Philips LCD TV and it works perfectly. The mount is heavy and holds the TV well. We have two adjacent rooms where we relax and this mount swivels easily around the corner so that was can view the TV in either room. I was a little skeptical using only two hex head lag bolts, but it holds the base mount solidly to the wall. Some of the reviews I read before purchasing it mention sagging, but I have no such problem with this mount. Using the extension arms, the holes on the back of the TV lined up and after tightening the screws, it was very solid as well. Make your connection first, then tighten. The bolt that attaches the TV to the mount arm just before the final step to adjust the position of the screen, seems a little small, but it holds. It took me about 20 minutes to install. For $29, it was a great buy. It comes with a variety of bolts to accomodate most mountings but I\'d skip using the enclosed wrench for a metric socket and good screwdriver.',5,'Very Good Buy',1371427200,'06 17, 2013'),(404,'A2C0L77SWTXMOV','0972683275','David',0,0,'After reviewing all the available mounts, double checking the whole patterns on the back of the TV, I decided this was my best option. It arrived in about 3 days, even though it said 7 when I ordered it. It took me about 20 minutes to install it. The package with the bolts and mounting hardware was very abundant with many sizes for length and thread size. I am certain that anyone else that is looking at this mount will be able to adapt it to there TV. It is very sturdy, stout, universal an