all plate is attached to the Arm with two Carriage Bolts / easy to remove and makes holding in place while bolting to the wall a breeze).Took me 1-1/2 hours from start (gathering my tools) to finish (hanging the TV)  Oh, and I\'m a 56 yr old disabled female.  I do have a  lot of construction/tool knowledge however.',5,'What\'s the word for better than great???',1379462400,'09 18, 2013'),(607,'ACS5A8NRVRQ8M','0972683275','JDR01930',0,0,'This is half the price and same quality of the Peerless ones I\'ve used in the past, and more mounting holes on the plate for to fit a wider ranges of VESA patterns.',5,'Great quality and price.',1392768000,'02 19, 2014'),(608,'AMZPGSUL2HJMQ','0972683275','JD\'S',1,1,'Does what it\'s intended for below pricing found on other brands. I have a 32\" mo nted in the bedroom with this. Seems sturdy emough for it...went up easily. Only reason for docking one star is the difficulty in adjusting the unit in the beginning. You really need (on my unit at least) to work it for a while before installing so you don\'t have to put so much stress on the mounts once installed. It was VERY stiff and took quite a bit of muscle to loosen it up enough to adjust...even with the adjusters loosened for this purpose...suppose it\'s better to have it too tight than loose and have the tv \"drift\" around.For $25.00 that I paid for a decent mount that has the range of angles...great find.',4,'Great value',1291680000,'12 7, 2010'),(609,'A1ELV5JOVFMNOV','0972683275','Jeanette',0,0,'Bought this to mount my Samsung 40\" in the corner of my bedroom and it works great. Very easy to install, seems very sturdy, and the range of motion of the arms for a corner mount is perfect.',5,'Easy Installation',1372550400,'06 30, 2013'),(610,'A1X7SF8S7VRCVH','0972683275','Jeanne M. Murray',0,0,'The price was great, it arrived quickly, installation fairly simple, but the wall mount is actually heavier than my 28\" tv!',4,'good, but heavy',1322438400,'11 28, 2011'),(611,'A3F0Y83DVO5T