er a month, our 32\" LCD is still mounted perfectly on our wall.',4,'Low price, works great.',1335312000,'04 25, 2012'),(617,'A19QVO6ZINIZHS','0972683275','jennifer chalker',0,0,'We liked this item so much we bought another one and then bought one for my step dad. Awesome product!',5,'Awesome',1358035200,'01 13, 2013'),(618,'A1QKUDP9EUHJXH','0972683275','Jennifer Ingberg',0,0,'Used this for the bedroom. Put it in the corner but was only able to hit the stud with a couple bolts.',4,'Insignia',1367193600,'04 29, 2013'),(619,'AELFAZJYOP332','0972683275','Jennifer Lynn',0,0,'Down to the point, I have a 42\" vizio! Yes! It looks great! Yes, it is wall stud efficient! Not extremely easy to move, but it definitely does the job!Now for my complaint! The box had nothing saying it was able to be used on wall stud. So I contacted warehouse seller to find out if it was capable. They got back to me only to tell me they had no idea. Now if a product is yours and you are selling it.. Shouldn\'t you know the details to it? After responding back to one email.. They stopped responding after! So then I had to return the product. I then re-ordered it after looking on reviews, an it does the job. I\'m complaining because I feel that if they knew their products detail, it would have saved me a lot of time and trouble.',4,'Great product for the money, but bad product knowledge',1360108800,'02 6, 2013'),(620,'A29Y8MLKEZILVU','0972683275','Jenny Dee',0,0,'Perfect for our bedroom! Can move TV against the wall or pull it out for viewing. Great product.  Highly recommend.',5,'Perfect!',1380672000,'10 2, 2013'),(621,'AV2AZD7ZIBC3L','0972683275','jenny',4,5,'small packaging. this mount was great! it was a great deal for this product easy installation we had it installed in 30 mins we sugggest to only use the three bolts down the middle thou cause if you used too many it can weaken the stud\'s holding power.',5,'sturdy and easy installation!',1289260800,'11 9, 2010'),(622,'A3W2CPHVD6E5QR','0972683275','jerbear1953',0,0,'Purchaed this for my Sons room, he loves being able to put the tv in any position he wants..As well as being able to fold it up to the wall.A five star for this item..The Price cant be beat.',5,'Videosecu Long Arm TV Wall mount Low Profile',1384732800,'11 18, 2013'),(623,'A3UTDVL4CPYCTW','0972683275','Jeremy Cather',0,0,'Easy to install and feels very secure. I bought two more for another two TVs I want to mount. Highly recommend it.',5,'Great product',1372204800,'06 26, 2013'),(624,'A3TAS1AG6FMBQW','0972683275','Jeri Zerr \"formerly a Road Warrior of the Nth...',0,0,'The VideoSecu line of articulating wall mounts has become our standard of choice for high quality articulating wall mounts within our home.  The value is such that the convenience of having an articulating wall mount for connecting or reconnecting cables is well worth the few bucks required to mount our HDTVs conveniently to the wall.  Highly recommend this great quality product. This wall mount will secure any of the HDTVs using the VESA 100 or VESA 200 mount pattern. We like to use a mount on the larger end than actually needed so if we later upgrade the HDTV with a larger size there\'s a much better chance we won\'t need to replace the articulating mount.',5,'High quality construction, comes with plenty of easy to install hardware.',1353456000,'11 21, 2012'),(625,'A20EHH02K9S2UZ','0972683275','Jesse Oliver',1,1,'The only issue that I have with this mount is that is only has 2 bolts to hold it into the wall.  I have a 55&#34; that it is holding, and I really don\'t feel that it is that secure.  I tightened everything the way the instructions say, though when moving the TV the mount was sliding against the wall with the weight of the TV.  I would suggest only using this one with a smaller TV than it\'s max of 55&#34;.  I tightened everything more, and it no longer moves against the wall, but I think the stud in the wall is now cracked.  Not good.',2,'2 bolts',1368144000,'05 10, 2013'),(626,'A1WXU0BY2L7ZL9','0972683275','J. Galloway \"Master Technologist\"',163,172,'This flat panel mount is adjustable and very cost effective, an excellent product for the money.  This arm comes with all needed mounting hardware for either masonry or wall stud mounting as well as a set of 4 screws for several sizes of panel mounting screws.  It also comes with a small wrench for two different sizes of hex heads on the arm and an allen wrench for one of the arm adjustments.  It is at least a two man operation to attach the flat screen after the arm is attached to the wall.  I mounted mine on a stud in the wall.  For stud mounting you use two of the six mounting hex head lag screws that come with it.  It doesn\'t say exactly in the directions but you should use a 1/4\" drill bit to pre-drill the holes in the stud.  I would not recommend trying to use the included hex wrench to tighten down the wall mounting lag screws, you need more leverage to tighten it than it provides; use a crescent wrench or other longer hex wrench.  I used a stud finder to locate the studs accurately.  Make sure you do not have obvious pipes or electrical going through the wall at the chosen location.  They can throw off some stud finders.  If you want to quickly adjust one of the arm adjustment screws it also contains a replacement screw that has a slip bar top lever so that it can be loosened and tightened without a wrench.  There is one optional cable management loop that attaches to the bottom of the middle of the arm.  It could use one more at the wall, but that is easy to improvise.  The flat panel we have is 32\" and 25 lbs. and works well for the mounting arm.I really like this product for this price.',5,'Excellent low cost movable arm',1286150400,'10 4, 2010'),(627,'A3QTXADA24F55O','0972683275','JG \"JG\"',0,0,'5 stars because it was an excellent purchase. It came with all the required parts, the assembly had clear instructions and was easy to install. I am using it for a Sony Bravia 32&#34;... I\'ve had it for 4 months so far and it works great.',5,'Great Product',1360627200,'02 12, 2013'),(628,'AYRACCER8JXU1','0972683275','J H',0,0,'Ok quality.  Good value.  I\'ve got the arm angled (not straight out) and the middle hinge DOES show some bend or flex.  Angle adjustments up/down are not the easiest to do, so this is not a good choice if you\'ll be adjusting your TV often.',4,'Ok quality, ok features, good value',1386460800,'12 8, 2013'),(629,'A2T4OX8NH9LIIC','0972683275','J. Hornback \"twister\"',0,0,'you can spend a ton of money on one of these, or you can buy this one.  hung a 32 inch tv with it with no problems.',5,'works great',1358553600,'01 19, 2013'),(630,'A3VSGMP5KCQ4Q2','0972683275','Jim A',0,0,'This is a really well made and engineered product which should be twice the price. It has every kind of leveling and tilting adjustment you could want, and a nice finishing piece that goes over the wall plate and lag bolts.  The mounting process can\'t be rushed and planning everything out before you start makes all the difference. Just make sure you find the middle of a wall stud for the lag bolts.It easily managed a 47&#34; led lcd which weighs 35lbs, and it might take the extra 10-12 lbs of a 55&#34; led lcd if it\'s not pulled too far from the wall. Since it can swing out over 20&#34; I\'d be carefull about going bigger than the 35lb 47&#34; tv that I mountedThe only thing which was dissappointing were the two plastic wire holders which are junk (very flimsy, one was broken in the package) and shouldn\'t be included when simple black wire ties work far better.',5,'Great quality tv mount at bargain price',1366243200,'04 18, 2013'),(631,'A1QKKD813YA5BJ','0972683275','JIM BATTLECAT',0,0,'This is the smallest articulating tv mount I have seen so far it is holding up a 40 inch flatscreen effortlessly and makes the room look bigger with out being noticable',5,'great',1360454400,'02 10, 2013'),(632,'A2RUN82QPU60PN','0972683275','Jimbo',0,1,