ough but it will not articulate as smoothly as some of the higher priced models.  Also, do not bother with the bubble level as it is cheaply made and will not provide an accurate reading.I will keep this one as I already mounted up the TV, but the next unit I buy will be a higher priced, easier to articulate mount.',3,'Okay for the money, but you get what you pay for',1310688000,'07 15, 2011'),(757,'A1GJHLL1Y090P5','0972683275','Lambirth',0,0,'This TV stand is being used for our 32\" Vizio. The hardware included was perfect and the stand bolted right up. I did need a socket and ratchet. Getting the TV into place however, was a bit more difficult. I recommend having a second person to install. One to hold the TV in place while another lines up and inserts the screws into the back of the TV. This wall mount is pretty strong, and seems to hold my TV\'s weight without any strain.',5,'Installed so fast!',1289692800,'11 14, 2010'),(758,'A1TTW3G7D18GS5','0972683275','LaRue',1,1,'It works great for our TV and was so reasonably priced compared to all the others we had looked at in stores.',5,'Mount',1359244800,'01 27, 2013'),(759,'A2FF6SG2Z15WY8','0972683275','Laura Austin',0,0,'Has been holding daughter tv up for couple years now it is good and strong 32 inch if your looking for something flat on wall this isn\'t what you want this sits a little off wall and can pull in and out must pull from both sides of TV may be difficult at times and you may have to secure bolts over time because pulling back and forth loosens up but they give you a tool keep it in safe place just for those times over all good product glad I got it.',4,'Good product',1395705600,'03 25, 2014'),(760,'A1EHAX7WGEJFEV','0972683275','Laura',0,0,'This tv mount is perfect for our granddaughters room. The price was amazing.  Much cheaper than any store around and great quality.',5,'PERFECT',1372636800,'07 1, 2013'),(761,'A2N7FW352FF8AQ','0972683275','Laura Nobach',0,0,'I was looking for an articulating wall mou