d it, another 5 holes later showed me where the edges were. I still ended up just missing, only getting 4 out of the 6 screws actually into the stud, but its solid with a 32\" LCD 28 pounder. The level it comes with is great- don\'t be afraid to take it apart to make installation easier.',5,'worth it',1325203200,'12 30, 2011'),(903,'A81NVWL4MMVT8','0972683275','nick m',0,0,'It works for the tv I bought but I had to use some of my own washers for the screws.  I thought it would have everything.',4,'Good',1380326400,'09 28, 2013'),(904,'A3BLYMV1UIDWU9','0972683275','Nicole82',0,0,'Great product, awesome price compared to store prices, highly recommend product,easy to install.  Good quality, matches most tv brands. Great bargain',5,'Great product great value',1356566400,'12 27, 2012'),(905,'A19NI7EG704QLJ','0972683275','Nikki',0,0,'Easy install and great design. The product was exactly what I thought it was going to be and just as as the picture shown.',5,'Great product',1318809600,'10 17, 2011'),(906,'A29N5GAYTJUFQM','0972683275','Nikki \"Nikki Lynn Allen\"',0,0,'The package came in time and everything was in the box. My boyfriend put it all together and it\'s been over a year and the tvs still hanging in the mudroom.',5,'Perfect',1382054400,'10 18, 2013'),(907,'A3EP4YIS9W1LR1','0972683275','Nitkad',0,0,'I have mounted a 42 inch old LCD. Easy to install. Easy to swivel, there is tilt option but it has to be locked by nuts(it can not be changed without loosing the nuts).',5,'Good for price',1358121600,'01 14, 2013'),(908,'AHPRCZ59P9RU0','0972683275','Nooga Shooter',0,0,'I wanted to put my mac in the wall and leave it. This does that well.  I don\'t move it often it seems strong and well built. If you want to move it a lot get something different you have to keep an Allen wrench and a crescent wrench in the desk drawer if you plan on moving it a lot. The articulation is sketchy. For my uses and the cheap price this was perfect.',5,'It works for me',1294704000,'01 11, 20